text: Cormac McCarthy is the American author (born 1930s). Cormac McCarthy also may refer to: * Other Americans: ** Cormac McCarthy (musician) (born c. 1950) * Line of and from ancient Irish leaders: ** Cormac mac Airt (fl. 2nd, 3rd, or 4th cen.) ** Cormac Laidir MacCarthy, Lord of Muscry and in 1446 re-builder of Blarney Castle ** Various monarchs of Desmond, and claimants to that line, in 12th to 21st centuries
title: Cormac McCarthy (disambiguation)
